{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DOMMatrixReadOnly: scale() method","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly/scale","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.DOMMatrixReadOnly.scale"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Geometry_interfaces\">Geometry interfaces</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly\"><code>DOMMatrixReadOnly</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly/DOMMatrixReadOnly\"><code>DOMMatrixReadOnly()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly/flipX\"><code>flipX()</code></a></li><li><em><code>scale()</code> </em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly/translate\"><code>translate()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Geometry Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrix\"><code>DOMMatrix</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMQuad\"><code>DOMQuad</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>scale()</code></strong> method of the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly\"><code>DOMMatrixReadOnly</code></a> interface creates a new matrix being the result of the\n  original matrix with a scale transform applied.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>scale()</code> method is specified with either one or six values.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>DOMMatrixReadOnly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scaleX<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nDOMMatrixReadOnly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scaleX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleY<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nDOMMatrixReadOnly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scaleX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleY<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleZ<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nDOMMatrixReadOnly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scaleX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleY<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleZ<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> originX<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nDOMMatrixReadOnly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scaleX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleY<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleZ<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> originX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> originY<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nDOMMatrixReadOnly<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>scaleX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleY<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaleZ<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> originX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> originY<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> originZ<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"scalex\"><a href=\"#scalex\"><code>scaleX</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A multiplier for the scale value on the x-axis.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scaley\"><a href=\"#scaley\"><code>scaleY</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A multiplier for the scale value on the y-axis. If not supplied, this defaults to\n      the value of <code>scaleX</code>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scalez\"><a href=\"#scalez\"><code>scaleZ</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A multiplier for the scale value on the z-axis. If this value is anything other\n      than 1, the resulting matrix will be 3D.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"originx\"><a href=\"#originx\"><code>originX</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      An x-coordinate for the origin of the transformation. If no origin is supplied,\n      this defaults to 0.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"originy\"><a href=\"#originy\"><code>originY</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A y-coordinate for the origin of the transformation. If no origin is supplied, this\n      defaults to 0.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"originz\"><a href=\"#originz\"><code>originZ</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A z-coordinate for the origin of the transformation. If no origin is supplied, this\n      defaults to 0. If this value is anything other than 0, the resulting matrix will be\n      3D.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>\n  Returns a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrix\"><code>DOMMatrix</code></a>\n  containing a new matrix being the result of the matrix x and y dimensions being scaled\n  by the given factor, centered on the origin given. The original matrix is not modified.\n</p>\n<p>If a scale is applied about the z-axis, the resulting matrix will be a 4âœ•4 3D matrix.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  This SVG contains three squares, one red, one blue, and one green, each positioned at\n  the document origin:\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">html</span></p><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 25 25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>red<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>transformed<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>transformedOrigin<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>25<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fill</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>green<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>\n  This JavaScript first creates an identity matrix, then uses the <code>scale()</code>\n  method to create a new matrix with a single parameter.\n</p>\n<p>\n  We test if the browser supports a six parameter <code>scale()</code> method by creating\n  a new matrix using three parameters and observing its <code>is2D</code> property. If\n  this is <code>false</code> then the third parameter has been accepted by the browser as\n  a <code>scaleZ</code> parameter, making this a 3D matrix.\n</p>\n<p>\n  We then create a new matrix scaled about a given origin, using either three or six\n  parameters depending on the browser support.\n</p>\n<p>\n  These new matrices are then applied to the blue and green squares as a\n  <code>transform</code>, changing their dimensions and position. The red square is left\n  in place.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> matrix <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DOMMatrixReadOnly</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> scaledMatrix <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> matrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> scaledMatrixWithOrigin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> matrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// if the browser has interpreted these parameters as scaleX, scaleY, scaleZ, the resulting matrix is 3D</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> browserExpectsSixParamScale <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span>scaledMatrixWithOrigin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>is2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>browserExpectsSixParamScale<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  scaledMatrixWithOrigin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> matrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\ndocument\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#transformed\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"transform\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaledMatrix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#transformedOrigin\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"transform\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> scaledMatrixWithOrigin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div><div class=\"code-example\" id=\"sect1\"><p class=\"example-header\"></p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Examples sample\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"http://localhost:5042/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly/scale/runner.html?id=examples\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.fxtf.org/geometry/#dom-dommatrixreadonly-scale","title":"Geometry Interfaces Module Level 1"}],"query":"api.DOMMatrixReadOnly.scale"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.DOMMatrixReadOnly.scale"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The scale() method of the\n  DOMMatrixReadOnly interface creates a new matrix being the result of the\n  original matrix with a scale transform applied.","popularity":0,"modified":"2023-05-19T17:19:46.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/dommatrixreadonly/scale","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/dommatrixreadonly/scale/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/37163d27e0625a83a3f8633fe58b9041867adeaa","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"scale()","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly","title":"DOMMatrixReadOnly"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrixReadOnly/scale","title":"scale()"}],"pageTitle":"DOMMatrixReadOnly: scale() method - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}